<h1>Waffles</h1>
<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
<li>2 cups all-purpose flour</li>
<li>1 tablespoon baking powder</li>
<li>1/2 teaspoon baking soda</li>
<li>1/2 teaspoon salt</li>
<li>2 eggs</li>
<li>2 tablespoons maple syrup</li>
<li>6 tablespoons vegetable oil</li>
<li>1 3/4 cups milk</li>
</ul>
<h2>Instructions</h2>
<ol>
<li>Combine flour, baking powder, baking soda, and salt in a large mixing bowl.</li>
<li>Add remaining ingredients and mix well until smooth.</li>
<li>Let batter rest for 5 minutes. Preheat the waffle iron during this time.</li>
<li>Cook in waffle iron according to your waffle iron instructions.</li>
</ol>
